Title: Crimebusters
Plot: An unconscious war widow and her lifeless infant are found in the rubble of a bombed army recruitment center; Jack McCoy is forced to make one of the most unpopular decisions of his career.
GuestStars: MacKenzie Mauzy, Christian Camargo, Michele Pawk, Amelia Campbell, Lisa Emery, Scott Sowers, Judith Hawking, Brian J. Smith
